statements: SELECT * FROM Manufacturing WHERE product_id = 1
SELECT product_name, quantity FROM Manufacturing WHERE price > 50
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT product_id, product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE quantity <= 10
SELECT product_name, quantity, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE price BETWEEN 20 AND 50
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Manufacturing
SELECT AVG(price) AS average_price FROM Manufacturing
SELECT SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM Manufacturing
SELECT MIN(price) AS min_price, MAX(price) AS max_price FROM Manufacturing
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE LOWER(product_name) LIKE '%apple%'
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE product_name IN ('Product A', 'Product B', 'Product C')
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE product_name NOT LIKE '%XYZ%'
SELECT product_id, product_name FROM Manufacturing WHERE product_name IS NULL
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_name) AS unique_products FROM Manufacturing
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE price > (SELECT AVG(price) FROM Manufacturing)
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE quantity = (SELECT MAX(quantity) FROM Manufacturing)
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Manufacturing WHERE quantity > 100)
SELECT product_name, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Manufacturing WHERE quantity < 10)
SELECT product_id, product_name, quantity, price FROM Manufacturing WHERE product_id % 2 = 0
SELECT * FROM Manufacturing.Part;
SELECT part_id, part_name FROM Manufacturing.Part;
SELECT * FROM Manufacturing.Supplier;
SELECT supplier_id, supplier_name FROM Manufacturing.Supplier;
SELECT Manufacturing.Part.part_id, Manufacturing.Part.quantity FROM Manufacturing.Supplier JOIN Manufacturing.Part ON Manufacturing.Supplier.part_id = Manufacturing.Part.part_id;

SELECT Manufacturing.Supplier.supplier_id, Manufacturing.Supplier.supplier_name, Manufacturing.Part.part_name FROM Manufacturing.Supplier JOIN Manufacturing.Part ON Manufacturing.Supplier.part_id = Manufacturing.Part.part_id;

SELECT Manufacturing.Part.part_id, COUNT(Manufacturing.Supplier.supplier_id) AS num_suppliers FROM Manufacturing.Part LEFT JOIN Manufacturing.Supplier ON Manufacturing.Part.part_id = Manufacturing.Supplier.part_id GROUP BY Manufacturing.Part.part_id;
SELECT * FROM Manufacturing.Part WHERE quantity > 100;
SELECT * FROM Manufacturing.Supplier WHERE supplier_name LIKE 'ABC%';
SELECT supplier_name, part_name FROM Manufacturing.Supplier JOIN Manufacturing.Part ON Manufacturing.Supplier.part_id = Manufacturing.Part.part_id;
SELECT MIN(quantity) AS min_quantity, MAX(quantity) AS max_quantity FROM Manufacturing.Part;
SELECT AVG(quantity) AS avg_quantity FROM Manufacturing.Part;
SELECT SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM Manufacturing.Part;
SELECT COUNT(part_id) AS num_parts FROM Manufacturing.Part;
SELECT supplier_name, COUNT(*) AS num_parts_supplied FROM Manufacturing.Supplier GROUP BY supplier_name;
SELECT part_name, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM Manufacturing.Part GROUP BY part_name;
SELECT supplier_name, COUNT(*) AS num_parts_supplied FROM Manufacturing.Supplier GROUP BY supplier_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT part_name, supplier_name FROM Manufacturing.Part JOIN Manufacturing.Supplier ON Manufacturing.Part.part_id = Manufacturing.Supplier.part_id ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT supplier_name, COUNT(*) AS num_parts_supplied FROM Manufacturing.Supplier GROUP BY supplier_name ORDER BY num_parts_supplied DESC;
SELECT supplier_name, COUNT(*) AS num_parts_supplied FROM Manufacturing.Supplier GROUP BY supplier_name ORDER BY num_parts_supplied DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT product.name, manufacturer.name FROM product JOIN manufacturer ON product.manufacturer_id = manufacturer.id;
SELECT product.name, production_line.line_name, quantity FROM product JOIN production ON product.id = production.product_id JOIN production_line ON production.production_line_id = production_line.id;

SELECT product.name, production_line.line_name, production_date FROM product JOIN production ON product.id = production.product_id JOIN production_line ON production.production_line_id = production_line.id;

SELECT product.name, production_line.line_name, quantity, production_date FROM product JOIN production ON product.id = production.product_id JOIN production_line ON production.production_line_id = production_line.id;
SELECT p.name AS product_name, m.name AS manufacturer_name FROM product p JOIN manufacturer m ON p.manufacturer_id = m.id;
SELECT p.name AS product_name, pl.line_name, quantity FROM product p JOIN production pr ON p.id = pr.product_id JOIN production_line pl ON pr.production_line_id = pl.id;
SELECT p.name AS product_name, pl.line_name, pr.production_date FROM product p JOIN production pr ON p.id = pr.product_id JOIN production_line pl ON pr.production_line_id = pl.id;
SELECT p.name AS product_name, pl.line_name, pr.quantity, pr.production_date FROM product p JOIN production pr ON p.id = pr.product_id JOIN production_line pl ON pr.production_line_id = pl.id;

SELECT p.name AS product_name, m.name AS manufacturer_name, pl.line_name, pr.quantity, pr.production_date FROM product p JOIN manufacturer m ON p.manufacturer_id = m.id JOIN production pr ON p.id = pr.product_id JOIN production_line pl ON pr.production_line_id = pl.id;

SELECT p.name AS product_name, m.name AS manufacturer_name, pl.line_name, pr.quantity, pr.production_date FROM product p JOIN manufacturer m ON p.manufacturer_id = m.id JOIN production pr ON p.id = pr.product_id JOIN production_line pl ON pr.production_line_id = pl.id LIMIT 10;

SELECT p.name AS product_name, m.name AS manufacturer_name, pl.line_name, pr.quantity, pr.production_date FROM product p JOIN manufacturer m ON p.manufacturer_id = m.id JOIN production pr ON p.id = pr.product_id JOIN production_line pl ON pr.production_line_id = pl.id WHERE pr.quantity > 100;
